name: Trader Bing's Cafe
description: Featuring their white cheddar mac & cheese, Trader Bing’s Café is serving up a variety of breakfast and lunch options, including sandwiches, salads and wraps, as well as your favorite Portland Roasting espresso, coffee and tea drinks. Conveniently located in the Austin Hall lobby.
address: Inside Austin Hall, 2751 SW Jefferson Way, Corvallis, OR 97331

name: Cascadia Deli
description: Choose from made-to-order sandwiches, rice bowls, grab-n-go items, and more at Cascadia Deli, located inside Cascadia Market. Try new specialty sandwiches weekly! Vegan and vegetarian options are available.
address: International Living-Learning Center, 1701 Western Blvd, Corvallis OR 97331

name: e.Cafe
description: Located in the Kelley Engineering Center main lobby, the e.Cafe menu includes breakfast, toasted sandwiches, gyros, smoothies, mac & cheese and pastries from local bakeries.  Portland Coffee Roasters is featured in the hand-crafted beverages, beside other creations with tea, matcha and chai.
address: Inside Kelley Engineering Center, 2500 NW Monroe Ave, Corvallis, OR 97331

name: Ava's Cafe
description: Ava’s Café, on the main floor of Linus Pauling Science Center, offers breakfast sandwiches, quesadillas, pasta alfredo, signature grilled sandwiches, smoothies, blended drinks, assorted pastries and a selection of grab-and-go items.  Proudly serving Portland Coffee Roasters coffee.
address: 2900 SW Campus Way,, Corvallis, OR 97330

name: Coffee Corral
description: Coffee Corral is the go-to location for BBQ sandwiches, salads and wraps using your choice of sauce. Also serves an all-day breakfast menu, pastries, and espresso drinks that feature Portland Coffee Roasters.
address: 700 SW 30th St,

name: West Side Grill
description: West Side Grill offers house-made breakfast favorites in the morning like eggs-your-way, pancakes and biscuits & gravy. Choose from a selection of breakfast items and artisan sandwiches at lunch, and build-your-own burger for dinner.
address: West Dining, 351 SW 30th St, Corvallis OR 97331

name: Five Four One
description: Five Four One serves the best of Pacific Northwest cuisine, with ingredients from local farms and campus gardens. Try daily chef-created entrees, house-made pasta and pizza, soups, sandwiches and desserts. All produce at Five Four One is organic and all ingredients are free of pesticides, high fructose corn syrup, and artficial dyes, flavorings and sweeteners.
address: McNary Dining Center, 1300 SW Jefferson Ave, Corvallis OR 97331

address: McNary Dining Center, 1300 SW Jefferson Ave, Corvallis OR 97331

name: Off The Quad
description: A quiet, sit-down meal location in the Memorial Union along the hallway between the main stairs and the MU Commons. Serving curated menu items that are adjusted seasonally, along with weekly specials. Currently featuring fresh-pressed juice, savory bowls, wraps, burritos and tortas. Breakfast menu includes fresh biscuits with house-made jams, avocado toast and acai. Kombucha, root beer, and Pastega nitro coffee on tap.
address: Memorial Union 114 Memorial Union,  Corvallis, OR 97331
